node.text: Sad sad couple... Sigh.. 好的不学。。
"You really should’ve stolen the whole book because the warnings come after the spells." applies to this quite well

The court heard that the unemployed couple needed money for their daily needs and that after watching Crimewatch, they found Carousell scams a good way to make money quickly.⁣
⁣
And scam they did, cheating almost S$10,000 from more than 30 victims.⁣
⁣
